  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "A remake of the first game, however adding a new graphical overlay, a new interaction mode, a revised soundtrack, a new character and an all new bonus chapter at the end.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
    {
      "text": "The player assumes the role of a junior high school student who is asked by an angel to locate a witch that has snuck into his school. In order to find the witch, he must search the suspects' bodies for a \"witch mark.\"",
